These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, drawing, magic-tricks, video-games
The people have 4 different jobs:  social-worker, freelancer, photographer, firefighter
1. the freelancer is on the left of the social-worker##1
2. the person who's hobby is board-games is the firefighter##1
3. the photographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the firefighter##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left of the social-worker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Hobby          | video-games | magic-tricks | drawing | board-games   |
| Job   | freelancer  | social-worker     | photographer   | firefighter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: mauve, coral, azure, light-blue
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: bellflower, daisy, dahlia, lily
1. the person who likes light-blue is the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who likes mauve is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes coral is on the right of the person who likes light-blue##1
4. the person who likes light-blue is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | azure | light-blue | coral | mauve    |
| Flower   | dahlia    | daisy      | bellflower | lily |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, cucumber, cabbage, plum
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, volleyball, badminton, golf
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person eating lettuce is the person who's sport is tennis##1
3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
4. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating plum##1
5. the person eating cabbage is on the left of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Food         | lettuce | plum | cabbage   | cucumber |
| Sport   | tennis   | badminton | golf | volleyball         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different games are played: chess, whist, bridge, canasta
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, daisy, daffodil, rose
1. the person who growsdaisy is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing whist is on the left of the person who growsdaffodil##1
3. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing chess##1
4. the person playing whist is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Game   | canasta | whist | chess  | bridge      |
| Flower         | daisy | rose   | daffodil | poppy |

