.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, scientific, family, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, ambient, r&b, dubstep
1. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
2. the fan of r&b is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the fan of ambient is on the right of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | family | scientific | mystery |
| Music-Genre    | classical       | dubstep | r&b | ambient     |

