.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, documentary, musical, time-travel
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, traveling, fishing
1. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
2. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | musical | family | documentary |
| Hobby           | skydiving      | traveling | fishing | chess    |

