.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, zombie, thriller, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: nigerian, british, pakistani, egyptian
1. the pakistani is on the far left##1
2. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching thriller movies is on the far left##1
4. the british is on the far right##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | zombie | spy | epic  |
| Nationality           | pakistani | nigerian | egyptian       | british |

