.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, swimming, ice-hockey, badminton
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, metal, reggae, disco
1. the fan of disco is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the fan of disco is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the fan of metal##1
5. the fan of pop is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | golf      | swimming | badminton |
| Music-Genre   | pop          | metal | reggae     | disco    |

