.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-9::.
City: san-francisco, hamburg, paris, boston
4 different games are played: scrabble, domino, monopoly, go
1. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
3. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1
5. the person playing go is on the right of the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |   3    |    4     |
| City   | hamburg    | paris       | san-francisco | boston   |
| Game     | domino | monopoly | go   | scrabble |

