3. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person who growsdaffodil##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |       3       |   4    |
| Flower    | amaryllis | daffodil  | iris | balloon-flower |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | fantasy | adventure          | scientific    |

