.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, boat, snowmobile, ship
City: nizza, venice, london, san-francisco
1. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the far left##1
5. the person driving the boat is the person traveling to london##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Transport      | snowmobile | boat  | helicopter | ship |
| City   | nizza  | london | san-francisco           | venice   |

