3. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing go##1
4. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person playing domino is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | subway | scooter | bus  |
| Game           | whist | snooker      | domino | go |

