.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: coral, emerald, purple, brown
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, bluemaster, siglo, ritmeester
1. the ritmeester-smoker is the person who likes coral##1
2. the bluemaster-smoker is on the left of the person who likes coral##1
3. the person who likes purple is the siglo-smoker##1
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the bluemaster-smoker##1
5. the person who likes brown is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Color   | purple | emerald  | coral | brown   |
| Cigar        | siglo | bluemaster | ritmeester    | prince |

