.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-17::.
4 different games are played: bridge, poker, canasta, backgammon
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, november, february, june
1. the person who's birthday is in june is the person playing canasta##1
2. the person playing bridge is the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in february##1
4. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1
5. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |    3    |   4    |
| Game   | poker      | canasta | backgammon | bridge |
| Birthday     | december | june    | february  | november |

