4 different games are played: poker, monopoly, whist, scrabble
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is baseball##1
2. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the person playing whist##1
3. the person playing whist is the person who's sport is soccer##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | lacrosse | soccer | baseball | sailing |
| Game   | scrabble     | whist    | poker      | monopoly   |

