.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, thriller, time-travel, animation
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: rose, orchid, marigold, tulip
1. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left of the person watching animation movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person watching animation movies is the person who growstulip##1
5. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | time-travel | thriller | animation   |
| Flower     | marigold  | rose    | orchid       | tulip |

 